# Marketing Content Guidelines

## Brand Voice
- Playful and interactive tone
- Developer-friendly language
- Focus on the "magic" of animations and React
- Emphasize simplicity and elegance

## Key Features to Highlight
- Interactive text toggling
- Smooth CSS animations
- React state management demonstration
- Modern gradient designs
- Responsive user interface

## Content Types
- Hero sections with call-to-action buttons
- Feature highlight lists with emojis
- Technical benefit descriptions
- Demo encouragement phrases

## Avoid
- Overly technical jargon in marketing copy
- Long paragraphs - keep copy concise
- Generic "hello world" descriptions
- Boring or static language
